                                       geschenkt ans <rs type="org" ref="#pmb298922">Wolf-Museum Eisenstadt</rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><date>22. VIII. 1937</date>.</p><p>1 Brief entnommen</p><p>1 Brief geschenkt an <rs type="person" ref="#pmb21647">Paul Marx</rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><date>15. VIII. 1936</date>.</p><p>1 Brief gegeben an <rs type="person" subtype="implied" ref="#pmb2173">Mutter</rs>, <date>15. VIII. 36</date>.</p></quote>« Das entspricht
